short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: View coverage data in Git repositories. Collect code coverage from manual tests running in the browser.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
1. Code Viewer

Shows code coverage & other metadata gathered by SeaLights.
Currently supports github.com, bitbucket.org, gitlab.com.

2. Manual Tests

Collects coverage from manual tests running in the browser.
